[section#polymorphic.dtor
    [:en] Destructors
    [:zh_CN] 析构函数
]

[%@lib@dtor polymorphic]
[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr ~polymorphic();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:mandates]
[:en] [`T] is a complete type.
[:zh_CN] [`T] 为完整类型

[para:effects]
[:en] If [`*this] is not valueless, calls [`allocator_traits<Allocator>::destroy(p)],
where [`p] is a pointer of type [`U*] to the owned object and [`U] is the type
of the owned object; then the storage is deallocated.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`*this] 并非无值，则调用 [`allocator_traits<Allocator>::destroy(p)]，
其中 [`p] 是指向所拥有对象的 [`U*] 类型指针，而 [`U] 是所拥有对象的类型；随后释放其存储。
[div:end]
